**Path in repo:** `configs/mywebapp.service`  
**Real path on server:** `/etc/systemd/system/mywebapp.service`

```ini
[Unit]
Description=My simple Python web app
After=network.target

[Service]
# Run the app as this user (change if your username is different)
User=praveena

# Directory where your web files live
WorkingDirectory=/home/praveena/mywebapp

# Full path to Python and command to start the HTTP server on port 8080
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 -m http.server 8080

# Restart policy if the process crashes
Restart=always
RestartSec=3

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target